{"tid":775691,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"男女之間真係會有純友誼?","createTime":"2018-08-11T11:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T22:30:28.000Z","uid":157097,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"68ec14b2766103bda8e6c013f9211d8c40b49fcf","tid":775691,"uid":157097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T11:07:39.000Z","msg":"個心好亂,好多問題,好多煩惱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢好主動揾我傾計  可能係佢性格好外向,健談? 我諗多咗?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時大家有身體接觸 我整古佢,講下笑話  佢都會打下我, 又會笑到肚痛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時一齊傾計傾到大聲講大聲笑, 搞到人地話我地係咪有路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟係咩一回事?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知道我係毒撚, 唔應該咁有自信,咁敏感, 咁認真...但我真係控制唔到自己既情感..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62473b48b13549858e8f3ab1fbea6094426328c2","tid":775691,"uid":162539,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T11:08:25.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"8717ac0f839cb10b42dd6f07bed68c49d3f67724","tid":775691,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T11:08:57.000Z","msg":"係你諗多左"},{"pid":"b0a35d2d447ac04515dc2ef074ec2df425d38687","tid":775691,"uid":27247,"like":26,"dislike":6,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T11:09:12.000Z","msg":"女對男會有<br />\n男對女唔會有"},{"pid":"a61b58273114bcb0d0788c212cb8f84666d398c1","tid":775691,"uid":53730,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T11:09:36.000Z","msg":"梗係有<br />\ncatgirl幾多朋友你睇下"},{"pid":"84248653f109816483450411ddf91ac594b31d0b","tid":775691,"uid":157097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62473b48b13549858e8f3ab1fbea6094426328c2","tid":775691,"uid":162539,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-1